  "prompt": "Who is Azor Ahai in Game of Thrones?",
  "response": "Azor Ahai is a legendary figure from the lore in George R.R. Martin's \"A Song of Ice and Fire\" series, which inspired the \"Game of Thrones\" television show. According to the prophecy, Azor Ahai is a hero destined to be reborn and save the world from darkness, often associated with combating the White Walkers and the \"Long Night.\"\n\nThe prophecy comes from the faith of R'hllor, the Lord of Light. It states that Azor Ahai will be reborn amidst smoke and salt, wielding a flaming sword called Lightbringer. Various characters throughout the books and the show have been speculated to potentially fulfill this prophecy, including Jon Snow, Daenerys Targaryen, and Stannis Baratheon, although there is no definitive answer as to who Azor Ahai is in the current published materials.",
